  title: "Why can\u2019t I just drag the lander sprite and add physics directly to
    it?"
  text: "Technically you can, but it\u2019s not best practice. By separating logic
    (parent GameObject) from visuals (child with sprite), you gain flexibility. You
    can swap visuals, change scale, or add effects without breaking gameplay logic."
